2. Upgrade the physics (Claude got close, but incomplete)

Gravity alone won’t hold.

You need a composite force model:

Core force equation (refined)

F_ij = A_ij / d²  –  R_ij / d^k  +  C_ij

Where:
	•	A_ij (attraction) = alignment × shared goals × trust history
	•	R_ij (repulsion) = value divergence × identity threat × competition
	•	d = distance in state space (beliefs, behavior, context)
	•	k > 2 → repulsion decays differently than attraction (important)
	•	C_ij (coupling term) = coordination effects (teams, systems, contracts)

👉 Key upgrade:
	•	Humans don’t just attract/repel — they synchronize, dampen, amplify

This turns your system from “gravity sim” into a coupled oscillator field

